# Phase 156: MES — Órdenes de Producción + Asignación de Colaboradores a Líneas/Turnos

## Análisis del Estado Actual del `mes_service`

### Arquitectura

El microservicio sigue **Clean Architecture** con repository pattern completo:

```
mes_service/
├── mes_app/
│   ├── api/v1/endpoints/     ← 10 routers (scan, dashboard, labor, downtime, work_order, sync, resource, shift, planning, production)
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── enums.py          ← WOType, WorkOrderLineType/Status, ProductionEventType, ProdIssueType
│   │   ├── handlers/         ← WorkOrderHandler (CQRS Command)
│   │   └── config.py
│   ├── domain/repositories/  ← 8 interfaces ABC (IProductionRunRepo, ILedgerRepo, ILaborRepo, etc.)
│   ├── infrastructure/
│   │   ├── repositories/     ← SQLAlchemy implementations
│   │   └── clients/          ← WMS adapter, MasterData client
│   ├── models/               ← 19 ORM models (MultiTenantBase)
│   ├── schemas/              ← Pydantic DTOs
│   └── services/             ← ScannerService, KPIService, ProductionService, ShiftService
```

